"""Test get_performance_key_list get with Array category."""
with mock.patch.object(self.perf, 'get_request', return_value=self.p_data.
    array_keys) as mck_request:
    key_response = self.perf.get_performance_key_list(category=pc.ARRAY)
    mck_request.assert_called_once_with(category=pc.PERFORMANCE,
        resource_level=pc.ARRAY, resource_type=pc.KEYS, payload={})
    self.assertEqual(key_response, self.p_data.array_keys)
